OL,3,CGrandmother died 'after nurses read
OL,4,Cwrong DNR form'
OL,6,FPat's daughter-in-law, Paula Dawson,
OL,7,Fsaid: "She went into cardiac arrest,
OL,8,Fthe hospital staff checked 'her
OL,9,F'records' and said she was DNR so she
OL,10,Fwas left to die.
OL,12,F"Five minutes later the staff realised
OL,13,Fthe wrong records had been checked and
OL,14,Fshe wasn't DNR. If she had been
OL,15,Fresuscitated who will ever know if she
OL,16,Fwould have survived."
