OL,3,CGrandmother died 'after nurses read
OL,4,Cwrong DNR form'
OL,6,FPaula, who lives with Pat's son John
OL,7,Fin Whitewell Bottom in , said alarm
OL,8,Fbells had rung when her husband had
OL,9,Fcalled her from the hospital to tell
OL,10,Fher about the DNR form.JShe said: "I
OL,11,Fsaid to him 'no she didn't have one,
OL,12,Fshe would have told us, but also,
OL,13,Fshe'd never been ill before, or in
OL,14,Fhospital, so she couldn't have had
OL,15,Fone.J"About 20 minutes after Pat died
OL,16,Fa senior nurse went to see John in the
OL,17,Ffamily room and said 'there's been a
OL,18,Fmix-up'."
