OL,3,CGrandmother died 'after nurses read
OL,4,Cwrong DNR form'
OL,6,FAfter Pat had died, John was sat in
OL,7,Fthe room with her when, on three
OL,8,Fseparate occasions, staff came into
OL,9,Fthe room and did not realise she had
OL,10,Fpassed away.
OL,12,FPaula said: "My husband was in the
OL,13,Froom with her, a junior doctor entered
OL,14,Fthe room asked what had brought them
OL,15,Fto A&E that day.
OL,17,F"He looked down at the bed and asked
OL,18,FJohn if she always looked like that.
