OL,3,CGrandmother died 'after nurses read
OL,4,Cwrong DNR form'
OL,6,F"John was shocked at the comment and
OL,7,Fexplained she had passed away. He
OL,8,Fcouldn't believe they didn't know.J"We
OL,9,Fthen also had another two occasions
OL,10,Fwhere people entered the room, one
OL,11,Flady asking for some leads to use and
OL,12,Fone who asked if they could take Pat's
OL,13,Fblood pressure.
OL,15,F"I told them they could try but it
OL,16,Fwouldn't do much good."
