OL,6,FWhile Paula and John insist they are
OL,7,Fnot embarking on a "witch hunt"
OL,8,Fagainst any individual employee, they
OL,9,Fhave raised concerns about staffing
OL,10,Fwithin the hospital.
OL,12,FPaul said: "A&E departments are very
OL,13,Fchaotic to the point mistakes are
OL,14,Fbeing made and people are dying".JA
OL,15,Fspokesperson for East Lancashire
OL,16,FHospitals NHS Trust said: "There are
OL,17,Fno words that will lessen the pain
OL,18,Ffelt by Mrs Dawson's family following
OL,19,Fher death.J"We offer our sincere
OL,20,Fcondolences and would be happy to talk
OL,21,Fto them about their concerns.
